SUMMARY:Eastside Entrepreneurs: Woodinville Tech Night — Where Founders\, Capital & Deep Tech Converge
DESCRIPTION:On Thursday\, February 5\, 2026\, Eastside Entrepreneurs convenes for a landmark evening in Woodinville\, Washington — a time when the region’s founders\, investors\, and operators gather around the emergence of a new Eastside innovation hub at the “Brewery”. \nThis is not a seasonal meetup. \nThis is the night Woodinville’s startup ecosystem steps into the spotlight. This event brings together entrepreneurs and capital partners who are actively building\, deploying\, and scaling real companies. \nExpect a room of Founders with MVP-grade or better products\, Operators managing enterprise customers\, Angel investors and advisors looking for real deal flow. \nThis evening is designed for connection with substance— not pitch decks\, not hype\, but the relationships that lead to partnerships\, investment\, and growth. \nAttendance is limited to 50 curated participants to preserve the quality of conversation and connection. \nEntry Options: \nBring A Wine Bottle or Two (to add to shared tasting)\nBuy a Ticket (online registration) – Link to buy here\n$20 at the Door \nFounder & Operator Showcases\nWe are inviting a select number of founders and operators to give short\, high-impact presentations (2 minutes) focused on: \nA product or platform already in the market\nA meaningful new initiative or expansion\nA real business pivot or growth inflection\nThis is not an idea stage forum. \nWe are highlighting people who are building in the real world. \nShare Your Passion: Apply to Present\nWe are looking for short\, inspiring presentations (1 slide\, 2 minutes) focused on new projects\, pivots\, or growth strategies your business is implementing as we transition from winter into spring. How are you evolving your business for 2026? \nWe welcome proposals from entrepreneurs at all stages who can provide value-driven content to their peers. \nSubmit Your Spring Startup Vision: Submit Your Spring Startup Vision
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/eastside-entrepreneurs-woodinville-tech-night-where-founders-capital-deep-tech-converge/
LOCATION:Torenthal Enterprises\, 14400 NE 145TH ST STE 302\, Woodinville\, WA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-30-095855.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Bellevue+Eastside Entrepreneurs":MAILTO:keith.mccall@pollensystems.com
END:VEVENT
