SUMMARY:PNW Battery Collaborative February 2026 Happy Hour
DESCRIPTION:​Join the PNW Battery Collaborative for the first happy hour of 2026 and a gathering of the Seattle battery community! Whether you’re deep in battery tech or just interested in learning more about our growing community\, this is a chance to hang out\, swap ideas\, and unwind together in a laid-back setting over a few drinks. \n​Location: Stoup Brewing Capitol Hill \n​​​This event is free and open to everyone\, drinks are not provided \n​​​​Have questions? Email rmoolgavkar@gmail.com\n​================================================ \n​​The Pacific Northwest Battery Collaborative (PNWBC) is community of battery entrepreneurs\, scientists\, policymakers\, and enthusiasts united to make the PNW the nation’s leading hub of battery innovation. Follow our LinkedIn page to learn about battery innovations/opportunities in the PNW and join the 1\,150+ other collaborators who subscribe to our events calendar.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/pnw-battery-collaborative-february-2026-happy-hour/
LOCATION:Stoup Brewing – Capitol Hill\, 1158 Broadway\, Seattle\, Washington
CATEGORIES:Meetups
