SUMMARY:Executive Roundtable: AI Fluency in Action
DESCRIPTION:95% of organizations still struggle to achieve ROI from AI despite a huge $30–$40 billion enterprise investment. \nWhat sets the successful 5% apart? These businesses have mastered AI fluency: aligning strategy\, people\, and processes to turn pilots into scalable\, revenue-driving solutions. \nJoin Wimmer Solutions’ Executive Roundtable to uncover the best practices that make AI adoption stick. Our experts will share: \nWhy most AI initiatives fail and how to avoid common pitfalls\nWhat the leaders do differently to accelerate ROI\nPractical steps to build AI fluency across your organization\nThis isn’t just theory. You’ll gain actionable insights from real-world success stories and learn how to position your business for measurable impact. \nSeats are limited. Reserve your spot today and lead the way in transforming your enterprise with AI.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/executive-roundtable-ai-fluency-in-action/
LOCATION:Wimmer Solutions HQ\, 1341 N Northlake Way\,\, Seattle\, WA\, 98103
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-23-093154.png
END:VEVENT
