SUMMARY:Live Recording: The GeekWire Podcast
DESCRIPTION:Join co-founders Todd Bishop and John Cook for a live recording of their weekly podcast. Since 2011\, GeekWire has served as the Pacific Northwest’s premier tech news source. Headquartered in Seattle’s Fremont neighborhood\, GeekWire provides an inside look at the giants and startups shaping the global economy. \nThe Main Event:\nTech Breakdown: Watch a live recording as the founders analyze the week’s biggest local and national tech headlines.\nFremont Roots: Hear from the team that has covered the region’s growth from the “Center of the Universe.”\nAudience Q&A: A dedicated session to ask Todd and John your questions about the future of tech.\nFREE for Chamber members! $15 for non-Chamber members. \nAttendees enjoy complimentary beverages from Fremont Brewing.
