SUMMARY:GeekWire Agents of Transformation: Presented by Accenture
DESCRIPTION:Don’t just witness the AI revolution. Lead it. \nAgentic AI isn’t just a buzzword — it’s the new engine of industry. Join GeekWire for Agents of Transformation: Inside the AI Shift\, an exclusive half-day summit designed for leaders exploring the move from simple automation to autonomous innovation. \n  \nFeaturing high-profile fireside chats and in-depth panels\, we’re moving past the hype to show real-world examples of how intelligent agents are redefining how we work\, create and lead. \n  \nThe inaugural event\, presented by Accenture\, builds on our acclaimed editorial series that spotlights how companies and individuals are using intelligent agents to boost productivity and drive innovation. Check out the series HERE. \n  \nFor information on sponsoring the event\, contact us at: events@geekwire.com.
