SUMMARY:Aviation Expo
DESCRIPTION:Aviation Expo is the new premier gathering for aviation enthusiasts\, collectors\, and spotters! The debut event will take place from July 8-11\, 2026\, at the DoubleTree by Hilton Seattle Tacoma International Airport (SEA). This event features an aviation marketplace with over 200 tables of airline/aviation collectibles for trade/sale\, Seattle aviation landmark tours\, plane spotting events\, an aviation career day\, workshops & seminars\, and MUCH MORE! Hotel booking and registration are now open on our website. Additional information such as preliminary tours\, vendor information\, and our show hosts. We will provide more updates and information as they become available.
